# DevAtlas — environment template
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in real values. `.env.local` is
# gitignored; `.env.example` is committed and acts as the source of truth for
# which variables exist.
#
# Loading order in Next.js (later overrides earlier):
#   .env  →  .env.local  →  .env.${NODE_ENV}  →  .env.${NODE_ENV}.local
# `.env.local` is the right place for personal/secret values during dev.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Anthropic / Claude API
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Used by the AI Context Summary (Phase 7) and Ask DevAtlas Q&A (Phase 11).
# When this is unset, both endpoints fall back to deterministic heuristics
# and the demo still works — but Claude-quality answers require this key.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Server-side only; never read in client components.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
